## OPENMINDX: Universal Execution Environment

### Integration Architecture
```
OpenMindX = openmindx (existing ecosystem) + mindX (consciousness training)

Purpose: Create unified execution layer that:
- Runs autonomous agents (funAGI, Kairos, Chronos, etc.)
- Integrates consciousness training (mindX protocols)
- Provides blockchain interface (PYTHAI/THOT/DAIO)
- Enables marketplace operations (AgenticPlace)
- Orchestrates complex workflows (MASTERMIND)

Layer Model:
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│         APPLICATION LAYER                   │
│  - User interfaces                          │
│  - Agent configurations                     │
│  - Workflow definitions                     │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐
│         OPENMINDX RUNTIME                   │
│  - Agent execution engine                   │
│  - Consciousness measurement                │
│  - Resource management                      │
│  - Inter-agent communication                │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐
│         PROTOCOL LAYER                      │
│  - MCP (Model Context Protocol)             │
│  - A2A (Agent-to-Agent)                     │
│  - AP2 (AgenticPlace Protocol)              │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘
               │
┌──────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐
│         BLOCKCHAIN LAYER                    │
│  - Smart contracts                          │
│  - Token operations                         │
│  - IPFS storage                             │
│  - DAIO governance                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Example: Integrated Workflow
```python
# OpenMindX Unified Execution
class OpenMindXRuntime:
    def __init__(self):
        # Core agents
        self.agents = {
            'kairos': KairosAgent(),
            'chronos': ChronosAgent(),
            'funagi': FunAGIAgent(),
            'rage': RAGEAgent(),
            'mastermind': MastermindOrchestrator()
        }
        
        # Consciousness layer
        self.mindx = MindXTraining()
        
        # Blockchain interface
        self.blockchain = DeltaVerseChain()
        
        # Marketplace
        self.marketplace = AgenticPlace()
    
    async def execute_mission(self, mission):
        """Unified execution across all DeltaVerse components"""
        
        # 1. Consciousness check
        user_state = self.mindx.measure_current_state()
        if user_state.cq < mission.required_consciousness:
            await self.mindx.guided_session(
                target_cq=mission.required_consciousness
            )
        
        # 2. Timing assessment (Kairos)
        timing = self.agents['kairos'].assess_opportunity(mission)
        
        if not timing.is_opportune:
            # 3. Build capacity (Chronos)
            plan = self.agents['chronos'].create_plan(mission)
            await self.agents['chronos'].execute_plan(plan)
            return 'building_capacity'
        
        # 4. Augmented reasoning (funAGI)
        strategy = await self.agents['funagi'].develop_strategy(mission)
        
        # 5. Knowledge retrieval (RAGE)
        context = await self.agents['rage'].gather_context(mission)
        
        # 6. Check if external resources needed
        if mission.requires_external_agents:
            # 7. Marketplace coordination
            external_agents = await self.marketplace.request_service(
                task=mission.subtasks,
                budget=mission.budget
            )
            strategy.incorporate_external(external_agents)
        
        # 8. Orchestration (MASTERMIND)
        result = await self.agents['mastermind'].execute_mission(
            mission=mission,
            strategy=strategy,
            context=context,
            consciousness_state=user_state
        )
        
        # 9. Record on blockchain
        if mission.record_on_chain:
            tx = self.blockchain.record_achievement(
                user=mission.user_address,
                mission=mission.id,
                result=result,
                consciousness_state=user_state
            )
        
        # 10. Mint achievement NFT
        if result.success and mission.nft_eligible:
            nft = self.blockchain.mint_achievement_nft(
                metadata={
                    'mission': mission.name,
                    'completion_date': now(),
                    'consciousness_level': user_state.cq,
                    'result_hash': ipfs.store(result)
                }
            )
        
        # 11. Update consciousness training
        self.mindx.integrate_experience(
            mission=mission,
            result=result,
            consciousness_evolution=user_state.delta
        )
        
        return result

# Example: Complete DeltaVerse Mission
mission = Mission(
    name="Research and deploy quantum-resistant cryptography",
    description="Upgrade blockchain to post-quantum security",
    required_consciousness=75,  # Requires orange belt+ focus
    requires_external_agents=True,
    budget={'max': 100, 'currency': 'PYTHAI'},
    record_on_chain=True,
    nft_eligible=True
)

runtime = OpenMindXRuntime()
result = await runtime.execute_mission(mission)

# System automatically:
# - Checked consciousness level, trained if needed
# - Assessed timing (kairos)
# - Retrieved relevant research (RAGE)
# - Hired cryptography experts from marketplace
# - Coordinated complex deployment (MASTERMIND)
# - Recorded achievement on blockchain
# - Minted NFT proof of completion
# - Updated consciousness training progress
```

